<h1 class="title">Sources: VAXXED Delta Pilot DIES IN-FLIGHT, Emergency Landing Required</h1>
<h2 class="subtitle">The Stew Peters Show</h2> <div class="article-byline">
<div class="meta-data"><p>By <span class="author"><a href="https://www.redvoicemedia.com/author/stewpetersshow/" title="Posts by Stew Peters Show" rel="author">Stew Peters Show</a></span> <br> <span class="date"><time class="date" datetime="2021-10-11">October 11, 2021</time></span></p></div>
